{"tid":1377333,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"(amazing summer) 邀請大家參加夏水禮","createTime":"2019-07-28T13:35:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T14:06:02.000Z","uid":285481,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1efbbd168e09bffdee2dc4b686c889209ae9a7a3","tid":1377333,"uid":285481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T13:35:52.000Z","msg":"大家好！宜家夏天咁熱最岩玩水戰！<br />\n小弟誠意邀請各位香港市民參與香城夏水禮<br />\n<br />\n夏水禮需要既四寶有：<br />\n<br />\n1. 氣球<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qz1ettG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQz1ettG.png&h=cd36b051&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2. 液體（隨意）<br />\n3. 投射器<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AxLrjAL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAxLrjAL.png&h=f65b40b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n4. 大型針筒<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rZL632L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrZL632L.png&h=1870e79a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n製作過程<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CArxZBu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCArxZBu.png&h=439228eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AiBFo3i.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAiBFo3i.png&h=67a2984e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zPxQMgE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzPxQMgE.png&h=b0bcbb73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n每一個投射器最少2-3人操作，記得約埋三五知己一team<br />\n有d負責reload d 氣球，咁就快手好多啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9z4Dk-TiPvk?t=49\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9z4Dk-TiPvk%3Ft%3D49&d=W0WGn%2FLYmVT4dQ5oB2FXDR%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=7a98db9d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9z4Dk-TiPvk?t=49</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-2BMJolRHk4?t=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-2BMJolRHk4%3Ft%3D19&d=W0WGn%2FLYmVT4dQ5oB2FXDR%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=9c02a01e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/-2BMJolRHk4?t=19</a><br />\n你哋睇吓啲鬼佬玩得幾開心，最遠可以射到幾十米架<br />\n<br />\n咁買左以上工具既朋友下次就可以一齊玩水啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBe water, my friend<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f27fd3e943a862920dff0b1e7d3d48ae89cc901","tid":1377333,"uid":285481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T13:41:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ogDMjJg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FogDMjJg.png&h=f80437fa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3xVCroh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3xVCroh.png&h=f1e7529c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇朋友一齊玩水啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50a6e0dac972ccd309115000885e024000e87e2f","tid":1377333,"uid":285481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T13:48:43.000Z","msg":"大家記得液體有好多種<br />\n有水、食油、甚至電油！<br />\n落食油分分鐘冼死人地對家⋯<br />\n而落電油啦wor，如果對面有人食煙或者<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">點火</span></span>，就好大劑㗎啦！<br />\n<br />\n大家唔好亂放野入去啊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87a1ae6d67c31c211d2adf60097265e4b9d03017","tid":1377333,"uid":285481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T13:49:35.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac7b4d4fd4d1fc1e453d0cf94a125565a1f